<p id="fs-idm176649728">Which base, CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>2</sub> or (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>NH, is the stronger base? Which conjugate acid, <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> or <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math>, is the stronger acid?</p></div></div>

