<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm117245200"><a class="os-number" href="chapter-14#fs-idm117245456-solution">41</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
<p id="fs-idm117244944">Predict which compound in each of the following pairs of compounds is more acidic and explain your reasoning for each.</p>
<p id="fs-idm117244432">(a) <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>HSO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>HSO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> or <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>HSeO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>HSeO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idp39171888">(b) NH<sub>3</sub> or H<sub>2</sub>O</p>
