<div class=" " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp33478144">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp33478400"><span class="os-number">42</span><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
<p id="fs-idp33478656">Rank the compounds in each of the following groups in order of increasing acidity or basicity, as indicated, and explain the order you assign.</p>
<p id="fs-idp33479200">(a) acidity: HCl, HBr, HI</p>
<p id="fs-idp33479584">(b) basicity: H<sub>2</sub>O, OH<sup>−</sup>, H<sup>−</sup>, Cl<sup>−</sup></p>
<p id="fs-idp33481376">(c) basicity: Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>, Si(OH)<sub>4</sub>, ClO<sub>3</sub>(OH) (Hint: Formula could also be written as HClO<sub>4</sub>.)</p><p id="fs-idm14022912">(d) acidity: HF, H<sub>2</sub>O, NH<sub>3</sub>, CH<sub>4</sub></p>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class=" os-hasSolution " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idm83972448">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm83972192"><a class="os-number" href="chapter-14#fs-idm83972448-solution">43</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
<p id="fs-idm83971936">Rank the compounds in each of the following groups in order of increasing acidity or basicity, as indicated, and explain the order you assign.</p>
<p id="fs-idm83971392">(a) acidity: NaHSO<sub>3</sub>, NaHSeO<sub>3</sub>, NaHSO<sub>4</sub></p>
<p id="fs-idm83969984">(b) basicity: <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>ClO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>ClO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>IO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>IO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idp33342400">(c) acidity: HOCl, HOBr, HOI</p>
<p id="fs-idp33342784">(d) acidity: HOCl, HOClO, HOClO<sub>2</sub>, HOClO<sub>3</sub></p>
<p id="fs-idp33343808">(e) basicity: <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> HS<sup>−</sup>, HTe<sup>−</sup>, <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>PH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>PH</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idp54362976">(f) basicity: BrO<sup>−</sup>, <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>BrO</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div></div>

