<p id="fs-idp68108976">From the equilibrium concentrations given, calculate <em data-effect="italics">K</em><sub>a</sub> for each of the weak acids and <em data-effect="italics">K</em><sub>b</sub> for each of the weak bases.</p>
<p id="fs-idp68111120">(a) NH<sub>3</sub>: [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 3.1 <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mo>×</mo></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
<math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>NH</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> = 3.1 <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mo>×</mo></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;</p>
<p id="fs-idp69240176">[NH<sub>3</sub>] = 0.533 <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;</p>
<p id="fs-idp69241568">(b) HNO<sub>2</sub>: <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> = 0.011 <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
