<p id="fs-idm1577296">[HNO<sub>2</sub>] = 1.07 <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;</p>
<p id="fs-idm1575904">(c) (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N: [(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N] = 0.25 <em data-effect="italics">M</em>;<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
