<p id="fs-idp58811680">Determine <em data-effect="italics">K</em><sub>b</sub> for the nitrite ion, <math display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>NO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>NO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow/><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> In a 0.10-<em data-effect="italics">M</em> solution this base is 0.0015% ionized.</p>
