<div class=" " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idm2126064">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm143472640"><span class="os-number">77</span><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
<p id="fs-idp15824512">Explain why a buffer can be prepared from a mixture of NH<sub>4</sub>Cl and NaOH but not from NH<sub>3</sub> and NaOH.</p>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class=" os-hasSolution " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idm81726160">
