<div class=" os-hasSolution " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp11460800">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm87207664"><a class="os-number" href="chapter-14#fs-idp11460800-solution">82</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
<p id="fs-idm165406368">What is [OH<sup>−</sup>] in a solution of 0.125 <em data-effect="italics">M</em> CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>2</sub> and 0.130 <em data-effect="italics">M</em> CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>3</sub>Cl?<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
